This is one definite way to lose all your friends in an instant - make a nuisance of yourself at the office or classroom with the Assault Rubber Band, where this drill is able to pump out rubber bands at your targets at unbelievable speeds. While it would deter any would-be attacker, once you've run out of ammunition, you'd best be prepared to make a quick getaway before your 'victims' gang up on you and give you a hiding you would love to forget down the road. So much for them saying they have a sense of humor...